From: '

Subject: RE: another Maxwell issue 
Date: Tue, 27 Apr 2021 16:42:41 +0000 
Attachments: SDNY PROD011 -  Overlay.zip 
Hello 
Attached is the overlay file that I got from the vendor. The overlay file contains the production number, file name and the 
MD5 Hash. Please let me know if there are any questions. 
Thank you. 
From: 
Sent: Monday, April 26, 2021 10:46 AM 
To: 
Subject: RE: another Maxwell issue 
< 
Thank you! The issue with production 11 is that defense counsel has expressed difficulty reviewing the metadata on the 
images contained in the production. In particular, the FBI created the attached spreadsheet, which listed the metadata 
the FBI was able to extract from the images, but defense counsel has indicated they have no way of knowing which bates 
numbered image in the production corresponds with which row in the spreadsheet. I'm hoping there's something in the 
production we can point them to that will help them match up each bates number with each row in the spreadsheet. 
From: 
Sent: Monday, April 26, 2021 10:33 AM 
To: 
Subject: RE: another Maxwell issue 
3 PM would be fine. Please send me the conference call information. 
Thank you. 
From: 
Sent: Monday, April 26, 2021 9:59 AM 
To: 
Subject: Re: another Maxwell issue 
< 
I'll be stuck in a meeting at 2pm. Would 3pm or later work, please?

wrote:

information regarding the issue with production 11? 
EFTA00025179

Thank you.
